guideos-keyring (1.0-3) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Simplified GPG key management
  * Install GPG key directly to /etc/apt/trusted.gpg.d/
  * Use ASCII-armored key format (.asc) for better compatibility
  * Remove obsolete keyring files
  * Add proper postinst and postrm maintainer scripts
  * Clean up configuration files on package purge

 -- Actionschnitzel <actionschnitzel@guideos.de>  Thu, 12 Dec 2025 12:00:00 +0100

guideos-keyring (1.0-2) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Add GuideOS repository configuration and GPG keys
  * Support for GuideOS Cinnamon, Trixie and Universe repositories
  * Use modern deb822 sources format
  * Include APT configuration to suppress modernize-sources warnings
  * Automatically remove old .list format repository files
  * Automatically migrate GPG keys from old to new location
  * Provide detailed installation feedback and status messages

 -- Actionschnitzel <actionschnitzel@guideos.de>  Thu, 25 Sep 2025 12:00:00 +0200